               <p>657. 
               
                  <persName id="t17840526-134-defend1230" type="defendantName">
                     CORNELIUS 
                     ROSE
                  <interp inst="t17840526-134-defend1230" type="surname" value="ROSE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-defend1230" type="given" value="CORNELIUS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-defend1230" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted, for that <rs id="t17840526-134-off590" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-off590" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-off590" type="offenceSubcategory" value="taxOffences"></interp>
               he on the <rs id="t17840526-134-cd591" type="crimeDate">9th day of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-134-off590 t17840526-134-cd591"></join> last, at the parish of <placeName id="t17840526-134-crimeloc592">Langston in the County of Southampton</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-crimeloc592" type="placeName" value="Langston in the County of Southampton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-crimeloc592" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-134-off590 t17840526-134-crimeloc592"></join>, feloniously did make an assault and affray on 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840526-134-victim1232" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Morze
                        <interp inst="t17840526-134-victim1232" type="surname" value="Morze"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17840526-134-victim1232" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17840526-134-victim1232" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-134-off590 t17840526-134-victim1232"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , then and there being an <rs id="t17840526-134-viclabel593" type="occupation">officer of the Customs</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-134-victim1232 t17840526-134-viclabel593"></join> within the limits of the port of Portsmouth, then being one of the ports of this kingdom, on board a ship called the Eagle, in due execution of his duty, and with a certain axe which he in both his hands had and held, feloniously did cut off the middle finger of the said 
                     <persName id="t17840526-134-person1233">
                        Richard
                         Morze
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1233" type="surname" value="Morze"></interp>
