                     </persName>
                  , and thereby unlawfully and feloniously did maim him against the form of the statute
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>A Second Count for feloniously assaulting the said 
               <persName id="t17840526-134-person1234">
                  Richard
                   Morze
               <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1234" type="surname" value="Morze"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1234" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1234" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             an officer of the said Customs, on board the said vessel, within the limits of the said port, in the due execution of his duty, and unlawfully and feloniously maiming the said 
               <persName id="t17840526-134-person1235">
                  Richard
                   Morze
               <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1235" type="surname" value="Morze"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840526-134-person1235" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
